column5: So you don't need a license to fish this weekend, what are your limits? Conservation or sport?

I wasn't sure everyone with me has licenses. We got surveyed by the ministry today as well.  Our biggest at the time was ten and a half inches.  I like to see my tax dollars at work a nice guy too.  What a dream job ride around on a sled and talk to everyone about fishing, I shoulda stayed in school.
